high_descs: Turn around and walk to the red trash bin near the kitchen counter
Pick up the wine bottle from the trash bin
Turn around and walk over to the fridge
Put the wine bottle in the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk back to the trash bin
Put the wine bottle in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled wine bottle in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the red trash bin on the ground.
Pick up the bottle out of the trash bin.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Put the bottle in the fridge, close the door and then open the door, pick up the bottle and then shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room to face the red trash bin.
Put the bottle in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bottle in a trash bin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the trash can on your left.
Take the bottle out of the trash can.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the bottle and take it out again.
Turn around and go to the trash can.
Put the bottle in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wine bottle in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and hang a left just before the counter to reach the red container on the wooden floor.
Pick up the green bottle from inside the tall red container.
Turn around and walk to the fridge ahead.
Put the bottle inside the fridge to the right of the top shelf, chill for seven seconds, remove the bottle from inside and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the tall red container ahead on the wooden floor.
Place the chilled bottle inside the tall red container towards the back left corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bottle inside a red container.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the red trash can.
Pick up the wine bottle from the trash can.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the wine bottle in the fridge, then pick the wine bottle back up and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the red trash can.
Place the wine bottle in the red trash can.
anns.task_desc: Return the wine bottle to the red trash can chilled.
